<% content_for :title do %>
    NeuEve Order Confirmation
<% end %>


<tr>
    <td class="content-block">
        <h1 class="aligncenter">$<%= @pdt_hash["payment_gross"] %> <%= @pdt_hash["mc_currency"] %> Paid</h1>
    </td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="content-block">
        <h2 class="aligncenter">Thanks for your purchase!</h2>
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>
            COVID-19 UPDATE: Due to the pandemic, as of 4/21/2020, our warehouse fulfillment is running behind
            schedule by about 2 business days from normal. Please expect a tracking number in 3 business days.
        </strong>
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>
            CIVIL UNREST UPDATE: Carrier Pickup Delays (as of 6/4/2020)
            <br>
            With continued civil unrest happening throughout the United States, our warehouse
            informed us that there may be a delay of 1-2 days for mail carriers picking up shipments.
            This is due to driver safety concerns, compromised routes from major
            roads, and freeways shut down by peaceful protestors and/or the police.
        </strong>
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        Help other customers by sharing your opinion and experiences:
        <a href="https://www.neueve.com/reviews?utm_medium=email&utm_source=internal&utm_campaign=order+confirmation">neueve.com/reviews</a>
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        Once your package is shipped, you will receive an email with your USPS tracking number. Add <a href="mailto:marketing@shipbob.com">marketing@shipbob.com</a> to your address book to prevent it from going to your spam filter.
    </td>
</tr>
<% if !@is_bv_user %>
    <tr>
        <td class="content-block alignleft">
            <strong>TIP:</strong>
            Taking calcium, vitamin D, and omega-3 supplements daily will help NeuEve work better.
            Learn more at:
            <a href="https://www.neueve.com/faq?utm_medium=email&utm_source=internal&utm_campaign=order+confirmation#supplements">neueve.com/faq#supplements</a>
        </td>
    </tr>
<% end %>
<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>TIP:</strong>
        Taking <a href="https://infl.tv/dY6y">d-mannose supplements</a> daily will help prevent UTIs.
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>TIP:</strong>
        If you are experiencing pelvic pain, using <a href="https://www.vuvatech.com/collections/frontpage/products/full-set-of-vuva-magnetic-dilators?rfsn=1742452.8d0e50">magnetic vaginal dilators</a> can help.
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>TIP:</strong>
        In hot weather, please refrigerate your package for 6 hours when you receive it, so it hardens.
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block alignleft">
        <strong>SUBSCRIBE and SAVE:</strong>
        Save 20% by getting a monthly subscription to NeuEve or ordering in packs of 4!
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td class="content-block aligncenter">
        <table class="invoice">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>Shipping Address:</strong>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><%= @pdt_hash["address_name"] %><br>
                    <%= @pdt_hash["address_street"] %><br>
                    <%= @pdt_hash["address_city"] %>, <%= @pdt_hash["address_state"] %> <%= @pdt_hash["address_zip"] %>
                    <br>
                    <%= @pdt_hash["address_country"] %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>Payment Date:</strong>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <%= @pdt_hash["payment_date"] %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>PayPal Transaction ID:</strong>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <%= link_to @pdt_hash["txn_id"], "https://www.paypal.com/activity/payment/#{@pdt_hash["txn_id"]}" %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>Order Details:</strong>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table class="invoice-items" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

                        <% (1..(@pdt_hash["num_cart_items"].to_i)).each do |i| %>
                            <tr>
                                <td><%= @pdt_hash["quantity#{i}"] %> x <%= @pdt_hash["item_name#{i}"] %></td>

                                <td class="alignright">$ <%= @pdt_hash["mc_gross_#{i}"] %></td>
                            </tr>
                        <% end %>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Shipping</td>
                            <td class="alignright">$ <%= @pdt_hash["mc_shipping"] %></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="total">
                            <td class="alignright" width="80%">Total</td>
                            <td class="alignright"> $<%= @pdt_hash["payment_gross"] %></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </td>
</tr>

